[1] To run in EACS mode (for dynamic channel change)
spectraldaemon eacs &

[2] To run in classifier mode in current channel -
spectraltool startscan
spectraldaemon classify & OR spectraldaemon &

Remember scan must be started separately as spectraldaemon does not start scan by itself unsless connected to the GUI.

[3] To run with the GUI

spectraldaemon channels minpwr -70 &

To see all the available options, "spectraldaemon help" will print detailed usage.
